    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进入未知</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《STAaRS》，这是一款独特的调查模拟游戏，您将扮演一名志愿者，负责揭开未知活动的面纱。在《STAaRS》中，您将进入一个虚拟房间进行24小时的测试，体验随机出现的奇异事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >调查并报告</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当检测到活动时，您将通过一个入口进入虚拟房间进行调查。您的任务是观察、分类并报告这些活动，这些活动分为四个主要领域：空间、时间、异常和现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >测试您的技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此模拟测试挑战您的观察能力和压力下的决策能力，为您准备应对真实场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22 种独特的神秘活动等您调查和揭示。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机事件的动态 24 小时测试（每次测试持续 25-30 分钟）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于门户的互动调查系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >详细的分类和报告机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式环境，旨在测试您的技能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《STAaRS》为您带来充满挑战和沉浸感的体验，每一个决策都至关重要。您准备好迎接未知了吗？</p>",
